emerge here and it's very small. It's not
a big pattern, just a small pattern. But I

00:10:34.790 --> 00:10:41.070
hope you'll see that it's a pretty cool
pattern. Okay, all right. So, what we're

00:10:41.250 --> 00:10:48.600
going to show you is we show a picture of
