00:12:17.210 --> 00:12:24.570
recessive deafness. Okay. And you're going
to see a big difference. What you're going

00:12:24.750 --> 00:12:29.830
to see is that these people don't just
depict how you handle the object, but they

00:12:30.010 --> 00:12:36.730
actually show what the shape of this tool
